title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Airbus A320 - Resolve the long beep/high tone
description:
In this how to we are going to look at what is causing the long beep/high tone being continuous played when flying the Airbus A320 with the A32NX when the autopilot is on. Probably everyone has experienced this and you might have spend already a lot of time resolving it. In this short video I will show you what is causing it and how you can fix it.
